{"title":"The Sklar Super Something Frameset is Available and Shipping Now","link":"https://bikerumor.com/sklar-super-something-gravel-atb-frameset-available-now/","date":1694785748000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something.jpeg\" alt=\"Adam Sklar with the Super Something\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Adam-Sklar-with-the-Super-Something-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Bozeman, Montana is home to frame builder Adam Sklar. But, a few weeks ago he was in Portland, Oregon for the MADE Show, and I finally got to meet him in person. We chatted about the Super Something and he was excited about it being ready to start shipping this month. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>I’m sure you remember <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sklar-super-something-review-gravel-atb-bike-the-radavist/\" target=\"_blank\">my review</a> of the Limited Edition <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Radavist</a> Sklar Super Something <a href=\"https://sklarbikes.com/collections/bikes/products/supersomething\" target=\"_blank\">gravel bike</a>. I really thought the Super Something really was, well…super special. Seriously, I will own one of these frames one day. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"614\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899-800x614.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something in the weeds\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899-800x614.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899-297x228.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899-120x92.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899-768x589.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-the-weeds-e1694712781899.jpeg 897w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Sklar Bikes</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Super Something is Sklar’s all-road/gravel frameset and it marks the brand’s first production model. Combining the 10 years of experience in custom frame building, it’s said to be the epitome of Adam’s design philosophy – balancing unbeatable function with distinctive form. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While Sklar has always been known for high-end custom framesets, with this Super Something production run, the aim is to bring Adam’s unique blend of that high-end bike design and craftsmanship to a larger, wider audience. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>We are so excited to have these framesets available again</em>,” says Adam Sklar. “<em>The feedback from SuperSomething riders has been overwhelmingly positive and we can’t wait to get more fun bikes out to more people</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sklar’s Super Something</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something gravel rig front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-front.jpeg 900w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something gravel rig\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-gravel-rig.jpeg 900w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This bike is ready for anything. Its versatile platform allows it to be set up how you want, run the Super Something with drop bars, flat bars, alt-bars… geared, or single speed. It can grow and change as your riding style ebbs and flows. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The frame is made with what Sklar says is the finest double-butted, heat-treated chromoly steel. It was designed around a 700x42c gravel tire with a 70mm stem and drop bars. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something with alt bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-with-alt-bars.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something single speed\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-single-speed.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Adam says that the Super Something “falls around 40% along the spectrum from a fat tire road bike to a mountain bike”. That basically means that the Super Something will take on many different build options. The frameset boasts a tire clearance of 700x55c (27.5×2.1) with rear spacing at 142x12mm and 100x12mm for the front. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725-800x523.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something in ocean blue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725-800x523.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725-297x194.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725-120x78.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725-768x502.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-ocean-blue-e1694712948725.jpeg 1197w\" /></a><figcaption>The Super Something in Ocean Blue</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"532\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-800x532.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something in honey dijon\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-800x532.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-297x197.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-768x510.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-in-honey-dijon-e1694712928673.jpeg 1276w\" /></a><figcaption>The Super Something in Honey Dijon</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Super Something is manufactured in Taiwan and comes in sizes 48cm to 60cm. It comes in two finishes, Ocean Blue and Honey Dijon. Pre-ordered bikes are now shipping, and limited inventory remains for new purchases through the <a href=\"https://sklarbikes.com/collections/bikes/products/supersomething\" target=\"_blank\">Sklar website</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sklar Super Something Frame Specs and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Super Something retail: $1599 (all frames ship with seatpost clamp and thru-axels)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Frame &amp; fork material: double-butted, heat-treated chromoly Steel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>142x12mm rear, 100x12mm font spacing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>27.2mm seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li>160mm post mount or flat mount rear, ISO front brake mount on steel fork.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The frame is also compatible with tapered carbon forks (not included)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Clearance for 700x55c or 27.5x 2.1” tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3 bottle cages, one under the downtube</li>\n\n\n\n<li>68mm BSA bottom bracket shell</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compatible with EC34mm/44mm headset, 1-1/8” steerer steel fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Clearance for up to a 44T single chainring</li>\n\n\n\n<li>External cable routing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rocker dropouts for adjustable chainstay length or single-speed</li>\n\n\n\n<li>If you want to run flat-mount brakes just get the flat-mount<a href=\"https://www.paragonmachineworks.com/hangers-inserts/adjustable-dropouts/12-mm-left-side-rocker-flat-mount-160-rotor-choose-color.html\" target=\"_blank\"> rocker </a>from Paragon Machine Works  and run the <a href=\"https://www.enve.com/product/adventure-fork/\" target=\"_blank\">Enve adventure fork</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Sklar Super Something Adam's personal bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sklar-Super-Something-Adams-personal-bike.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sklar Super Something Geo</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image.png\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"335\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-800x335.png\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-800x335.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-297x124.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-120x50.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-768x322.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image-1536x643.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/image.png 2028w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://sklarbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SklarBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sklar-super-something-gravel-atb-frameset-available-now/\">The Sklar Super Something Frameset is Available and Shipping Now</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2e96d481c1dc58d6cb3e85d7232e069325a16d476404b0c8149f61435839f561","category":"Cycling"}